WEBVTT

00:08:29.965 --> 00:08:32.393
and everyone learned Spanish instead?

00:08:32.417 --> 00:08:33.988
Would you have cried?"

00:08:34.012 --> 00:08:35.266
And they all said no.

00:08:36.065 --> 00:08:39.238
They weren't crying because
of the communication barrier,

00:08:39.262 --> 00:08:41.580
they were crying because the man was deaf.

00:08:42.421 --> 00:08:43.763
But I see it differently.

00:08:44.493 --> 00:08:48.990
What if the Borg showed up in that video,

00:08:49.014 --> 00:08:53.228
and the Borg said,
"Deafness is irrelevant."

00:08:53.252 --> 00:08:54.978
Because that's what they say, right?

00:08:55.002 --> 00:08:56.476
Everything's "irrelevant."

00:08:56.500 --> 00:09:00.063
And then the Borg
assimilated the deaf guy --